description: Yellow Kitty is a wrestler on the Ultimate Surrender site. Up until her last match she wore a mask to hide her identity. Before this last match she was so confident she would win that she promised she would take off her mask and shoot for Hogtied if she lost. Well, thanks to Isis she was demasked and here she is, revealed for everyone! Yellow Kitty is a true bondage virgin. The first thing you notice about her is her smoking hot, sexy, amazing body. She did okay for a very first timer, don't you think?
title: Yellow Kitty
